Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未发现针对诺德拉姆的攻击迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这显然是有意图的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的目的多半不是摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是完好无损地夺取诺德拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么防卫部队足够应对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以集中全部兵力攻击敌人要塞？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 而且敌人的战略
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能更加大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与诺德拉姆强行对接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们所处的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了准备与诺德拉姆对接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切便说得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须赶紧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伯特小队 科尔小队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应对敌舰哨机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩余部队暂时保持距离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织突击阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人防守严密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来很难摧毁抵御光子环阵列的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫队全员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起 我指挥你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即汇合一处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会战斗 不论敌人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这机动…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他明明不是X-R
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要 打败你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败你 保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赢不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法完全成为战士的你！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今非昔比了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂兵全给我死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要失去冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没队长那么成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电磁终端 开始在轨道部署
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会不会一再光顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至多只能发射一到两次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部署还要多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使改变角度发射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这样还是会被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能指望明日野司令了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射线轴上发现敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的极有可能是攻击电磁终端
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽调机动战士来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也要守住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据推测那是要塞姿态控制系统的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座要塞为抵御攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行了整体调头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说 掩体只能防御来自固定方向的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为求直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有先打坏姿态控制系统
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间不多 我马上开始使用祖法尔特火箭炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围敌人就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引住敌人就是了对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝 维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞行动受限
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可以对其造成伤害 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 实施光子爆破炮的指向发射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人要塞 紧急转向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被防御的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 使用机动战士的推进器转动要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达 确实敌你不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让精神头盔满负荷运转…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙不要命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算得了什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为维甘指引未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达孜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何我也要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非实现不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令 您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我回天神号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们重新组织后 返回战线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子环阵列的防线岌岌可危
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支撑不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 请暂时中断发射程序
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把光子爆破炮的目标设定权交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔中士 让出操作席
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知全体机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤离射线轴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输入完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮发射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干涉掩体机能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲击造成推进系统重创
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人机动战士开始撤退后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有机动战士暂时撤离敌人要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待进一步指示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 总算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人要塞的推进系统完全停转
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此下去会和诺德拉姆相撞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即通知诺德拉姆政府紧急避难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人要塞失去了盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定用光子环阵列毁了它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 连射可能造成舰船无法航行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不发射的话诺德拉姆就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有放手一搏
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就现在 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮 指向发射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键时刻能量不足…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号动力室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入炮击后功率调整模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人要塞移速放缓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在偏离与诺德拉姆的撞击轨道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向本舰飞来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往左紧急避让
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 准备应对撞击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会和敌人要塞一同坠入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落地面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难免造成巨大伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先逃离要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 集结舰队全力应对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有作用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用光子爆破炮打开突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 发射系统部件损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要更换发射口侧面的共振控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上去换
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更换零件？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…明白了 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 情况明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离进入大气层 还有180分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更换完成 这样随时可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴们的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让你们一死了之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事 滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾米 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾米 等着我 马上来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…看来回不去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想和奥布莱特成为一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…孤单一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号是我们的家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说好要回家的 一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是我们的家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾米… 蕾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠落…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去地球会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆来电
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 还有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进入内部 引爆能量核心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以赶在坠入大气层前破坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 难道想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我 可以救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只有我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一度不知为何而战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被焦躁和仇恨冲昏头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 现在我已不再迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心只想保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请允许我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 如此下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座达乌内斯会对地球造成严重危害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 只能执行备案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 要塞自爆装置失去控制
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我想办法搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 直接去能量核心？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照备案 将登陆胶囊投放地球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须在要塞爆炸同时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混在残骸中 投放胶囊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看准时机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 请交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球是伊甸之地 必须救它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有控制的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-R之力 让我尽情使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算从内部摧毁这座要塞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 你休想阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但内部构造复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入深处的话 会来不及返回
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用高达撞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要引爆能量核心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用卫星摧毁器 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是能量核心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我指示引爆位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可能失败的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道伊泽尔坎特大人一早就打算这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到又能并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为维甘的战士 我战斗至今
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为实现维甘的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事与愿违
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人的力量 实在太过渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至于
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是救了许多人的性命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这只是想保住我们伊甸的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球是…伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们决心建造伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为战争和疾病受苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你战斗的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经连自己为何而战也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋里装满了对你和父亲的嫉妒心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你身在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置身险境
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也成了战士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有事需要你去完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞碎片因爆炸进入低空轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对地球的影响降低到最小限度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时确认高达逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入射角固定 进入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号随行进入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救亚瑟姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能扔下AGE系统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我信了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想开创的 维甘的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.49,0:22:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.73,0:22:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 为争夺这美丽的自然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在进行战争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.74,0:22:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此赤红的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.56,0:22:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到
